1
00:00:32,299 --> 00:00:34,730
I won't allow Junior Sister Su Yao to marry Gu Changsheng.

2
00:00:34,730 --> 00:00:36,000
She and I are true love.

3
00:00:36,230 --> 00:00:37,630
I'm taking her away today.

4
00:00:37,630 --> 00:00:40,600
Even the Imperial Clan can't stop us from being together.

5
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:41,530
What's going on?

6
00:00:41,630 --> 00:00:43,630
Did I just transmigrate?

7
00:00:46,260 --> 00:00:48,160
Congratulations to the host for successfully transmigrating.

8
00:00:48,160 --> 00:00:50,100
Injecting memories into the host.

9
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,460
Current world:

10
00:00:51,460 --> 00:00:52,430
Immortal Path of Ten Thousand Realms,

11
00:00:52,430 --> 00:00:54,930
a satisfying novel where various big shots compete to pamper the female lead.

12
00:00:54,930 --> 00:00:56,600
As the Patriarch of the Gu family,

13
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:58,200
I have the cultivation of a Quasi-Emperor.

14
00:00:58,200 --> 00:01:00,060
But my son is a villainous simp.

15
00:01:00,230 --> 00:01:02,030
He dug out his Dual Pupils for the female lead,

16
00:01:02,030 --> 00:01:04,260
and was killed by her and the Child of Fortune.

17
00:01:04,260 --> 00:01:05,300
The entire Gu family was wiped out.

18
00:01:05,300 --> 00:01:05,730
That's right.

19
00:01:05,730 --> 00:01:07,460
According to the original plot,

20
00:01:07,460 --> 00:01:08,330
it is currently

21
00:01:08,330 --> 00:01:10,600
the day of your son and the female lead's engagement ceremony.

22
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:13,060
The Child of Fortune, Lin Fan, is about to crash the wedding.

23
00:01:13,060 --> 00:01:14,030
Awesome.

24
00:01:15,860 --> 00:01:17,560
You want to crash the wedding?

25
00:01:17,830 --> 00:01:18,060
Yes.

26
00:01:18,060 --> 00:01:20,360
I'm taking Yao'er away today,

27
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,860
and no one can stop me.

28
00:01:21,900 --> 00:01:23,500
What is your cultivation level?

29
00:01:23,500 --> 00:01:25,100
Mid-Foundation Establishment.

30
00:01:25,100 --> 00:01:25,900
And me?

31
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,000
Uh,

32
00:01:27,030 --> 00:01:27,860
Quasi-Emperor.

33
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:28,700
So,

34
00:01:28,700 --> 00:01:29,960
you're saying

35
00:01:30,060 --> 00:01:33,030
you want to take her away right under my nose?

36
00:01:33,030 --> 00:01:34,229
Even if you are a Quasi-Emperor,

37
00:01:34,229 --> 00:01:36,100
you can't forcefully separate us!

38
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:37,560
Although I am no match for you now,

39
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:38,430
the tables

40
00:01:38,430 --> 00:01:39,130
will turn!

41
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:39,430
No.

42
00:01:40,830 --> 00:01:42,890
I'm going to teach you a lesson today.

43
00:01:42,960 --> 00:01:43,259
What

44
00:01:43,259 --> 00:01:44,500
lesson?

45
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:46,460
Respect the dead.

46
00:01:54,229 --> 00:01:55,600
Master, save me!

47
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:56,400
Stop!

48
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:57,830
No!

49
00:01:57,830 --> 00:01:58,830
Master!

50
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:12,030
Brother Lin Fan!

51
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:17,100
Plundered Heavenly Destiny Fortune,

52
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:18,260
999 points.

53
00:02:18,260 --> 00:02:20,130
Obtained Heavenly Destiny Halo.

54
00:02:25,930 --> 00:02:28,130
System, if I kill the female lead now,

55
00:02:28,130 --> 00:02:29,130
what will happen?

56
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:31,200
The host may attract great unseen danger,

57
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:32,360
leading to the collapse of the Heavenly Dao.

58
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,800
The female lead has an extraordinary background.

59
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,300
I understand.

60
00:02:34,300 --> 00:02:35,460
In the original plot, the female lead

61
00:02:35,460 --> 00:02:38,430
was indeed related to a supreme faction in the Immortal Realm.

62
00:02:38,430 --> 00:02:38,829
System,

63
00:02:38,829 --> 00:02:41,960
use all my Heavenly Destiny Fortune to upgrade my stats.

64
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:49,600
Gu Linyuan, you actually killed Brother Lin Fan!

65
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:50,829
He is the first person in eternity

66
00:02:50,829 --> 00:02:52,530
to break the curse of the Desolate Holy Body!

67
00:02:52,530 --> 00:02:53,600
You will suffer great retribution!

68
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:54,400
Retribution?

69
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,329
I am your retribution.

70
00:02:59,829 --> 00:03:01,800
Gu Linyuan, even if you are a Quasi-Emperor,

71
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,160
you can't force this!

72
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:05,030
Gu Changsheng and I are not in love at all.

73
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:06,360
I have fused the Dual Pupils

74
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,830
and become a natural Supreme Being.

75
00:03:07,830 --> 00:03:09,030
Just give me time.

76
00:03:09,030 --> 00:03:10,260
So what if you are a Quasi-Emperor?

77
00:03:10,260 --> 00:03:12,300
I will trample you underfoot in the future!

78
00:03:12,300 --> 00:03:13,230
True love?

79
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:16,560
Then what about the dual-pupils my son dug out for you

80
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:18,800
and the countless treasures given to you over the years?

81
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,060
What do they count for?

82
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,800
He gave them to me voluntarily.

83
00:03:25,060 --> 00:03:25,829
Did I force him?

84
00:03:25,829 --> 00:03:27,060
How dare she say that?

85
00:03:27,130 --> 00:03:28,360
If it wasn't for Mr. Gu's support,

86
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,800
how could she and the Su family have come to this today?

87
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,460
You know the Gu family is an imperial clan.

88
00:03:31,460 --> 00:03:32,829
The Su family ancestors didn't even produce a saint.

89
00:03:32,829 --> 00:03:34,400
She has no right to step into this hall.

90
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,329
So noisy.

91
00:03:36,829 --> 00:03:38,760
You want freedom and true love.

92
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,260
Fine.

93
00:03:41,100 --> 00:03:42,530
I will grant your wish.

94
00:03:43,660 --> 00:03:45,829
But what does not belong to you,

95
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:48,160
you should leave behind.

96
00:04:07,330 --> 00:04:08,830
No! Don't!

97
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:10,400
These are my eyes!

98
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:11,530
My dual-pupils!

99
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:13,560
I am a born supreme being!

100
00:04:14,430 --> 00:04:15,430
No!

101
00:04:15,900 --> 00:04:19,060
The fortune that could grow to the Immortal King stage in the original plot...

102
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:19,930
Bring it to me.

103
00:04:20,329 --> 00:04:21,899
Refined instantly.

104
00:04:35,860 --> 00:04:37,590
Throw her back to the Su family.

105
00:04:38,060 --> 00:04:39,600
And tell Su Changkong,

106
00:04:40,130 --> 00:04:41,200
that in three days,

107
00:04:41,630 --> 00:04:43,460
I will wash the Su family in blood.

108
00:04:43,460 --> 00:04:44,530
Yes, Patriarch.

109
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,560
According to the original plot given by the system,

110
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:50,000
Su Yao's mother is also someone with great fortune,

111
00:04:50,100 --> 00:04:51,500
who came from the Immortal Realm.

112
00:04:51,500 --> 00:04:53,630
Out of gratitude for Su Changkong's years of care,

113
00:04:53,630 --> 00:04:55,400
she has always stayed in the Su family.

114
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:57,159
If I want to break through to the Emperor Realm,

115
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:59,159
the opportunity should lie with her.
